{"tid":1436391,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"不如開個突發台俾d 記者會同突發現場post","createTime":"2019-08-09T09:40:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T11:05:05.000Z","uid":20563,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"95b8d6be062c5e29c448d3e1ee740dfbbc6e630e","tid":1436391,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:40:22.000Z","msg":"而家好多時d 記者會，尤其政府錄音機同克警記者會恥笑post, 會上曬熱門。 仲要係同時間幾個post, 其他post 就會俾記者會洗走曬<br />\n<br />\n所以建議開個突發台，將d 記者會post 放曬入去，開多個突發台熱門，咁巴絲可以睇返記者會d 野。當有示威突發野時，大家都可以係突發台現在update. 而係而家其他台既post 同熱門，可以show 返非突發台d 野<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1. 唔會因為記者會而洗走d post<br />\n2. 真係突發都易d 睇到post<br />\n3. 突發台熱門同一般熱門分開可以更清晰"},{"pid":"9ecdeb4a1642b0b18b260a22f96928c89277c139","tid":1436391,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:43:00.000Z","msg":"大家點睇"},{"pid":"71863e1a2ae531e7aa3bfa57036045d628d0cf6c","tid":1436391,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:47:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa9d4aaa3a1c0a7e5dd320007da282ba533d6a26","tid":1436391,"uid":4050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:52:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>點解一定係佢地開主題我地曬時間去駁佢？ 點解唔係我地開主題佢地之後回應我地</strong>？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔想知<span style=\"color: green;\">鐳射筆，外國勢力，大台</span><br />\n<br />\n想知<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>葉虎，同志們，過期彈呀</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"e10cbf0a66aeb863922e907535bc6ef1a23dd1ae","tid":1436391,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa9d4aaa3a1c0a7e5dd320007da282ba533d6a26","tid":1436391,"uid":4050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTi